---

cp2020-augmented is a companion module for the unofficial Cyberpunk 2020 game
system for Foundry VTT. It extends, but does not include, that system's code.
Any third-party assets or vendored code bundled with this module (for example
the Carolingian UI sheet skin) remain under their own original licenses. The
Cyberpunk 2020 tabletop RPG is the intellectual property of R. Talsorian Games.
